 scantest beginnings of his experiences traveling in Mumbai and Hyderabad, India.  In the lounge, we consider the &lt;a href="http://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2012/03/the-daily-shows-advantage-over-the-msm-an-eye-for-the-absurd/254836/"&gt;unique advantages of satire&lt;/a&gt; in the Daily show, as well as an interesting story highlighting how, if you're rich and clever enough, you &lt;a href="http://science.slashdot.org/story/12/03/22/1825242/blackjack-player-breaks-the-bank-at-atlantic-city"&gt;can indeed break the bank&lt;/a&gt;.
