/11/adobe-audition-moves-to-mac-with-cs5-5-soundbooth-eol/"&gt; Adobe moves to a subscription model and drops Soundbooth&lt;/a&gt; (thankfully), &lt;a href="http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5jIlTm5MhYuKmEp0gQs4y3FmrCjvQ?docId=CNG.36db2129cefe2fddf937f948acfab92b.661"&gt;human brains are more malleable than one might think&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href="http://search.slashdot.org/story/11/04/05/2238227/Google-Loses-Autocomplete-Defamation-Case"&gt;Google is liable in Italy for defamation from search results&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
